# Catalog output. Everything under site/public/ is generated from repository files by
# scripts/build-index.mjs, and site/dist/ is the built frontend. Committing either lets a
# stale copy be served after a plugin changes — the one failure the catalog must not have.
# Both are rebuilt on every PR and on every deploy. See docs/SITE-SPEC.md.
site/public/
site/dist/

# tsc -b incremental state. Machine-local, and it records absolute paths.
*.tsbuildinfo
